4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T15:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵貓舍千奇唔好搵Dolly Chiny<br />\n閪到一個點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打介唔介意講下點閪法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：打算係呢間排</blockquote><br />\n未比錢之前 佢會同你講有三次睇貓機會<br />\n比左訂金之後 問佢有冇得親身睇下貓b<br />\n佢又話唔得住等揀個陣先<br />\n好啦到揀貓(send email, 佢個玩法係一send出黎幾個人鬥快搶)<br />\n<br />\n問佢邊隻痴人d 答我same same<br />\n咁問有冇得睇<br />\n擾釀左一陣話有個唔駛睇既人揀左<br />\n好啦咁再問 下次揀可唔以睇<br />\n佢話返我轉頭 個個都唔駛睇係得我要睇<br />\n又話逐個睇好麻煩要好多時間<br />\n問多幾句 仲send張揸緊車既相比我<br />\n應該想表達叫我收聲<br />\n<br />\n唔知以為我乞緊佢施捨隻貓比我<br />\n本地買都無得睇 我不如訂外國breeder 仲要態度閪<br />\n<br />\n唔信既話留tg我send對話圖比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f924efed2f7fe5a0b9cec8492dbd3ca5e98ea12","tid":426221,"uid":29500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:01:30.000Z","msg":"between 香港有賣布偶貓既貓舍我差唔多問過晒<br />\n雖然我最後無買<br />\n但態度好、睇落可靠既有呢幾間，比你參考下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DiamondRagRagdoll/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDiamondRagRagdoll%2F&d=rqsymna4lTNBF1zk3sksWcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=748ce1f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DiamondRagRagdoll/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/asteridoll/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fasteridoll%2F&d=rqsymna4lTNBF1zk3sksWcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=10612cff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/asteridoll/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/michaelcatcattery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmichaelcatcattery%2F&d=rqsymna4lTNBF1zk3sksWcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=3f197a02\" data-auto-link target=